To the extent possible under law, the authors have waived all copyright and
related or neighboring rights to the adrkit decision record schema.

Full text: https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/legalcode

Rationale: the schema is intended to function as a shared contract. Competing
and independent implementations should be able to adopt it with no license
consideration whatsoever. See ADR-0006.
